{"tid":1477151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃台之瓜, 何堪再摘, 快文宣","createTime":"2019-08-16T04:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T08:58:57.000Z","uid":19817,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbebf993c19c44d94983fb112e35c06eb0b85f4","tid":1477151,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"事實上，「黃台之瓜，何堪再摘」是受政治逼害的李賢，在臨死前對當權者武則天作出的絕命詩。<br />\n<br />\n李賢其實是武則天與唐高宗的兒子，但唐高宗死後，武則天為實現稱帝的夢想，一嘗達到權力頂峰的滋味，多番逼害自己的兒子。在李賢之前，已害死了李賢的哥哥李弘，而李賢最後亦未能倖免，被武則天逼令自殺。<br />\n<br />\n李賢在死前寫下著名的《黃台瓜辭》，全詩為﹕<br />\n<br />\n「種瓜黃台下，瓜熟子離離。<br />\n一摘使瓜好，再摘令瓜稀。<br />\n三摘尚自可，摘絕抱蔓歸。」<br />\n此詩的意思，是以黃台之瓜比喻唐代的宗室，實在不堪受到一次又一次的採摘。李賢借此勸告母親武則天，不要再對自己的子女趕盡殺絕。<br />\n<br />\n這既非唐代盛行的絕句或律詩，而是採用古詩的體裁，卻廣為後世所知，後人更把此詩與三國時曹植的《七步詩》相提並論，同樣是勸告當權者不要再逼害自己的家人。"},{"pid":"5497efc6c9ed55b68d47630aa58dd7bc1140927c","tid":1477151,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ed4a87c5d1ba032df5c1623de4a929b74b0e43","tid":1477151,"uid":42820,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:49:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>因果由國<br />\n容港治己</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d63eaec3af38b86f92d9541ed9ab34c0ad6bd64b","tid":1477151,"uid":294916,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"236a104d9f1bbe254adc5f19b0912a9cf0cf876d","tid":1477151,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認真理性討論post 大家幫手入嚟投票</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Set死線通牒林奠再升級係大多手足嘅共識 大家入嚟公投同討下啦 要過5,000正評 民間記者會應該要反映到抗爭者主流意見同策略</span> </span><br />\n冇網絡大軍同P牌不能好評 要靠大家！！<br />\n<br />\n【公投】民間記者會設限825通牒林奠答應訴求（係答應唔係回應！！！）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEHHFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEHHFS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1cac86dfe314b8a630a7ee604fa2b1273eef0032","tid":1477151,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b15ca3343fb8963d2d25f67fee3d729b449634","tid":1477151,"uid":92017,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"777 = 武則天<br />\n誠哥姓李 = 唐代宗室都姓李<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbace1fe6406e89e41a0a3e49ac369526b29df43","tid":1477151,"uid":121255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"多謝誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e823a90eb7e6663ade2ba395e4bb71987f2cf71","tid":1477151,"uid":217455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"即係林鄭要迫死李家宗親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93139947ecc9f673fd6fb7df7c555e20ee75efac","tid":1477151,"uid":14494,"like":0,"